# Full Database Schema — FSA Capstone 2026
> ✅ **Confirmed applied to Azure PostgreSQL** — 2026-03-10 01:41 ICT  
> 61 Liquibase changesets · 28 tables · Spring Boot v4.0.2 · PostgreSQL 17.8

---

## Loại 1: ERD Level (Logical ERD)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    %% ── ACCOUNT & PROFILE
    account ||--o| user_profile           : "1-1 profile"
    account ||--o{ refresh_token          : "has tokens"

    %% ── CONTENT HIERARCHY
    dialect   ||--o{ level                : "levels"
    level     ||--o{ challenge            : "challenges"
    error_tag ||--o{ level                : "focuses on"
    error_tag ||--o{ placement_rule       : "rule for"
    dialect   ||--o{ placement_rule       : "targets"
    level     ||--o| level                : "parent/draft (self)"
    challenge ||--o| challenge            : "parent/draft (self)"

    %% ── CLASSROOM
    account       ||--o{ classroom        : "educator owns"
    classroom     ||--o{ classroom_member : "has members"
    account       ||--o{ classroom_member : "student in"

    %% ── PRACTICE & ATTEMPTS
    account          ||--o{ practice_session           : "starts"
    account          ||--o{ attempt                    : "makes"
    practice_session ||--o{ attempt                    : "contains"
    challenge        ||--o{ attempt                    : "tested via"
    attempt          ||--o{ attempt_phoneme_feedback   : "phoneme detail"
    attempt          ||--o| educator_feedback          : "educator review"

    %% ── BADGE
    badge   ||--o{ account_badge : "earned"
    account ||--o{ account_badge : "earns"

    %% ── FE-04: ACHIEVEMENT & BADGE SYSTEM
    achievement ||--o{ account_achievement  : "tracked for"
    account     ||--o{ account_achievement  : "progresses"
    challenge   ||--o{ daily_challenge      : "selected as daily"
    dialect     ||--o{ daily_challenge      : "scoped"
    daily_challenge ||--o{ account_daily_challenge : "completed by"
    account         ||--o{ account_daily_challenge : "completes"
    attempt         ||--o| account_daily_challenge : "result linked"

    %% ── FE-05: LEADERBOARD
    leaderboard ||--o{ leaderboard_entry : "has rankings"
    account     ||--o{ leaderboard_entry : "ranked in"
    classroom   ||--o| leaderboard       : "classroom board"
    dialect     ||--o| leaderboard       : "dialect board"

    %% ── FE-05: TOURNAMENT
    tournament ||--o{ tournament_participant : "has participants"
    account    ||--o{ tournament_participant : "joins"
    dialect    ||--o| tournament             : "scoped"

    %% ── FE-05: SOCIAL
    account ||--o{ friendship : "sends request"
    account ||--o{ friendship : "receives request"

    %% ── AI PREDICTION
    account   ||--o{ prediction : "receives"
    challenge ||--o{ prediction : "for"

    %% ── CONTENT WORKFLOW (approval-less in entity but tracked in history)
    content_approval_history }o--o{ account : "actioned by"

    %% ── ANALYTICS
    daily_analytics }|--|{ account : "aggregates"
```

---

